# ============================================================================
# SILAT AGENT ORCHESTRATOR - KUBERNETES DEPLOYMENT
# ============================================================================
# 
# Complete production-ready Kubernetes manifests including:
# - Namespace and RBAC
# - Secrets and ConfigMaps
# - Deployments and Services
# - HPA and Resource Quotas
